..TEXT:
The angelic strewing has reminded commentators, at least since
the time of Daniello (comm. to vv. 19-21), of the strewing of palm
fronds in the path of Jesus on what became known as Palm Sunday.
..TCHR:
194
..AUTH:
..PUBL:
..EDTR:
..ATTR:
